      <body>If you come across this error, it's because you're not flushing the log output. Use this which will automatically flush the log on every log call:

   Rails.logger.auto_flushing = true</body>
      <body-html>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you come across this error, it's because you're not flushing
the log output. Use this which will automatically flush the log on
every log call:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Rails.logger.auto_flushing = true&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</body-html>
